item.title: Wattamolla from Above 4K - Wherever I may Drone Episode 4
item.description:
Wattamolla from Above 4K - Wherever I may Drone Episode 4

Wattamolla - Royal National Park - Sydney Australia. Spectacular Sunrise at Wattamolla on Monday Morning the 25th of April 2016. The spare batteries for the DJI can't come soon enough. 20 minutes flight time is just not enough when you have scenery like this to explore...

item.title: Georges River - Como
item.description:
Georges River - Como

Sunset near Como Pleasure Grounds taken from 120m above sealevel using my DJI Phantom 4 - 5 Stitch Pano

item.title: Wherever I May Drone - Episode 1 - Home Sweet Home
item.description:
Wherever I May Drone - Episode 1 - Home Sweet Home

So I did it. I bought myself a drone. It's what you do when you have a midlife crisis, but can't afford a Tesla. I bought the new Phantom 4 from DJI and it is an incredible bit of gear. Really well built and it is incredibly easy to fly.
